<section>
<name>Setting the Keys Initially</name>
<t>Describe how the keys are derived from the DTLS master key and set.</t>
</section>

<section>
<name>Updating the Keys</name>
<t>Describe how the extended key update specified in
<xref target='I-D.ietf-tls-extended-key-update'/> is used.
In particular, describe when the new receive key is installed, the new send
key is installed and how the old receive key is removed. Same for the restart
keys. Describe how the key derivation is done.</t>
</section>

<section>
<name>Post Handshake Authentication</name>
<t>Describe how post handshake authentication as specified in
<xref target='RFC9261'/> is used.
